\"hkgmoji\" />雖然好多人話明日香係傲嬌既始祖，但Tv版既明日香同現今傲嬌又不盡相同<br />\n<br />\n利申：純個人見解，不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ace7a794a9fbb033c41757261554b8ab0c15c98","tid":1923044,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"我又係啱啱先第一次追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9daae5db9f62b27f43bc0f9d758b804eaac6c90","tid":1923044,"uid":215898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df3995ee8dabb51c15ed8e7706fc820b575a1c39","tid":1923044,"uid":44598,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"一班有自殺傾向既廢老揾全人類陪葬既計劃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"係咪好似共濟會光明會咁囉"},{"pid":"5b9d29cf1eba9f3e962618aa0828de0d6f89688f","tid":1923044,"uid":215898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df3995ee8dabb51c15ed8e7706fc820b575a1c39","tid":1923044,"uid":44598,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"一班有自殺傾向既廢老揾全人類陪葬既計劃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"係咪好似共濟會光明會咁囉"},{"pid":"2ca02f7479889f5f943d3094352363881bd8ee1e","tid":1923044,"uid":268486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:19:53.000Z","msg":"動畫界既王家衛"},{"pid":"ed48033334d6e596da364180cf4f1e571d3f84f8","tid":1923044,"uid":268486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"應該話動漫界既東邪西毒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b4a553c36c3215b900f871fe2310cf0a62f2e6","tid":1923044,"uid":69994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:36:09.000Z","msg":"原來真嗣是一個自閉症兒童，EVA的出現及二者的經歷，所有事都只是真嗣自己的幻想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f715c68168608968d7d9603c75603864